Working with the keyboard in the ECB-windows
============================================

   ECB offers the `ecb-mode-map' which binds the most important
functions of ECB to keys so you can easily use ECB without a mouse.

   IMPORTANT: Do not modify `ecb-mode-map' directly! The option
`ecb-key-map' defines all ECB keybindings, including a common prefixkey
(This is by default `C-c .'). If there are conflicts with other
minor-modes or packages you can define very easy another prefix.
Please read carefully the description of `ecb-key-map'!

* Menu:

* Navigation::
* Incremental search::


