Package avoid.el
================

   With GNU Emacs 20.X ECB must deactivate `mouse-avoidance-mode' if the
option `ecb-show-node-info-in-minibuffer' activates for at least one
ECB tree-buffer 'if-too-long or 'always. This is done automatically but
only as long ECB is activated.


